{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/create-a-custom-heading","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"bootstrap","demoType":null,"title":"Kreiraj prilagođeni naslov sekcije","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kreiraćemo jednostavan naslov sekcije za Cat Photo App postavljanjem naslova vesti i slike opuštenog mačka u istoj liniji.</p>\n<p>Zapamtite, Bootstrap koristi prilagodljiv sistem mreže koji olakšava postavljanje elemenata u redove i određivanje širine svakog elementa u odnosu na druge. Klasu za sisteme mreža Bootstrap može koristiti <code>div</code> element.</p>\n<p>Poredajte svoju prvu sliku i vaš <code>h2</code> element unutar jednog <code>&#x3C;div class=\"row\"></code> elementa. Poredajte svoj <code>h2</code> element unutar <code>&#x3C;div class=\"col-xs-8\"></code>, a svoju sliku unutar <code>&#x3C;div class=\"col-xs-4\"></code> kako bi bili u istoj liniji.</p>\n<p>Pogledajte kako slika sada odgovara adekvatnoj veličini koja se poklapa sa tekstom?</p>\n</section>","id":"bad87fee1348bd9aede08845","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":16816,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/create-a-custom-heading"},"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lobster\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n  h2 {\r\n    font-family: Lobster, Monospace;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .thick-green-border {\r\n    border-color: green;\r\n    border-width: 10px;\r\n    border-style: solid;\r\n    border-radius: 50%;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n  <h2 class=\"text-primary text-center\">CatPhotoApp</h2>\r\n\r\n  <a href=\"#\"><img class=\"img-responsive thick-green-border\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\r\n\r\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"Tuxedo cats running on dirt ground.\">\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n      <button class=\"btn btn-block btn-primary\">Like</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n      <button class=\"btn btn-block btn-info\">Info</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n      <button class=\"btn btn-block btn-danger\">Delete</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <p>Things cats <span class=\"text-danger\">love:</span></p>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>catnip</li>\r\n    <li>laser pointers</li>\r\n    <li>lasagna</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <p>Top 3 things cats hate:</p>\r\n  <ol>\r\n    <li>flea treatment</li>\r\n    <li>thunder</li>\r\n    <li>other cats</li>\r\n  </ol>\r\n  <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\r\n    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\"> Indoor</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\"> Outdoor</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Loving</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Lazy</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Crazy</label>\r\n    <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\r\n    <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\r\n  </form>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vaš <code>h2</code> element i najgornji <code>img</code> element treba da budu postavljeni zajedno unutar <code>div</code> elementa sa klasom <code>row</code>.</p>","testString":"const row = document.querySelector('div.row');\r\nconst h2 = row?.querySelectorAll(`:scope ${'h2'}`)\r\nconst image = row?.querySelectorAll(`:scope ${'img'}`)\r\nassert.lengthOf(h2,1);\r\nassert.lengthOf(image ,1);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš najgornji <code>img</code> element treba da bude postavljen unutar <code>div</code> elementa sa klasom <code>col-xs-4</code>.</p>","testString":"const column = document.querySelector('div.col-xs-4');\r\nconst div = column?.querySelectorAll(`:scope ${'div'}`);\r\nconst img = column?.querySelectorAll(`:scope ${'img'}`)\r\nassert.isEmpty(div);\r\nassert.lengthOf(img,1)"},{"text":"<p>Vaš <code>h2</code> element treba da biti postavljen unutar <code>div</code> elementa sa klasom <code>col-xs-8</code>.</p>","testString":"const column = document.querySelector('div.col-xs-8');\r\nconst div = column?.querySelectorAll(`:scope ${'div'}`);\r\nconst h2 = column?.querySelectorAll(`:scope ${'h2'}`)\r\n\r\nassert.isEmpty(div);\r\nassert.lengthOf(h2, 1);"},{"text":"<p>Svi <code>div</code> elementi bi trebalo da imati zatvarajuće oznake.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code,/<\\/div>/g);\r\nassert.match(code,/<div/g);\r\nassert.equal(code.match(/<\\/div>/g).length,code.match(/<div/g).length);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/#bootstrap","dashedName":"create-a-custom-heading","certification":"front-end-development-libraries","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"bootstrap","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null}],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/add-font-awesome-icons-to-our-buttons","prevChallengePath":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/use-a-span-to-target-inline-elements","id":"bad87fee1348bd9aede08845","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<!-- Code below this line should not be changed -->\r\n<div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n  <h3 class=\"text-primary text-center\">jQuery Playground</h3>\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\r\n      <h4>#left-well</h4>\r\n      <div class=\"well\" id=\"left-well\">\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target1\">#target1</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target2\">#target2</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target3\">#target3</button>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\r\n      <h4>#right-well</h4>\r\n      <div class=\"well\" id=\"right-well\">\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target4\">#target4</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target5\">#target5</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target6\">#target6</button>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/create-a-custom-heading"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}